{{Top|leg}}
'''Defensus Solar''' was a private [[Law enforcement agency/Legends|law enforcement corporation]] who were hired by the [[Geelan]] to maintain law and order aboard [[Zirtran's Anchor/Legends|''Zirtran's Anchor'']].<ref name="Zirtran's Anchor (article)">{{JournalCite|5|Zirtran's Anchor (article)}}</ref>

Operating from a conglomeration of interconnected warships in [[Sector Beta]], a force of 100 well-trained [[Defensus Solar Security Officer]]s frequently patrolled the [[Space station/Legends|space station]]. They were committed to their job and submitted all new arrivals to ''Zirtran's Anchor'' to a security and ID check before allowing them aboard the space station.<ref name="Zirtran's Anchor (article)" />

They did not mediate disputes between factions and were also not allowed into "independent zones", which were off limits to anyone but their owners and those the owners allowed aboard. Often [[Smuggler/Legends|smugglers]] and criminals would use independent zones as a way to get around Defensus Solar's agents. In an attempt to counter this, Defensus Solar set up random checkpoints hoping to catch such unauthorized visitors.<ref name="Zirtran's Anchor (article)" />

